data.value: Vazovo Eco Path is located in Stara Planina, near Svoge. It has two ends - one is near Bov Station and the other one reaches the village of Zasele. The ecopath is partly renovated. It passes over the Iskar River and the Treskavets River, past the Sts. Petka and Skaklya waterfall.
